document.full_text: al jazeera television reported on wednesday that an army helicopter had landed near a hospital in egypt's red sea resort of sharm el-sheikh where hosni mubarak was admitted to take the former president to cairo.
document.title: helicopter to take egypt's mubarak to cairo: report
